summary: I saw this fountain today which depicted a titan being buried in rocks and he had one in his hand and he looked like he was...
body: I saw this fountain today which depicted a titan being buried in rocks and he had one in his hand and he looked like he was going to throw it and I had a vivid and terrifying flash of Dan posting an ig story with a picture of it and a caption reading “Yes, stone me fountain daddy” and I have so many regrets in my life.
